            The Promise
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="the-promise__grid">
          <div class="the-promise__content">
            <p>Did you know that every 100 gms of Chicken you eat adds up to {{number}} of GHG Emissions of CO2,
              {{value}} of trees, and {{value}} of water? We have still not considered the run-off from an Industrial
              grade animal/poultry farm into our precious soil and groundwater that can eventually reach us! Add to
              that, the price we pay for healthcare!</p>
            <a class="btn btn--border-green" href="http://">EXPLORE <span class="arrow-right"></span></a>
          </div>
          <div class="the-promise__image-end">
            
              {% image "src/images/food-2.jpg", "", "Chicken Curry in bowl", "(min-width: 30em) 50vw, 60vw" %}
            
          </div>
          <div class="the-promise__image-start">
            
